    <link href="http://luminoid.github.io/blog/2017/06/08/Hexo-Common-Problems/"/>
    <id>http://luminoid.github.io/blog/2017/06/08/Hexo-Common-Problems/</id>
    <published>2017-06-08T12:25:08.000Z</published>
    <updated>2017-06-09T05:48:07.000Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<!-- toc -->
<a id="more"></a>
<h2 id="hexo-server-not-found"><a href="#hexo-server-not-found" class="headerlink" title="hexo server not found"></a>hexo server not found</h2><p><strong>Problem</strong>: Can’t find <code>hexo server</code> command.<br><strong>Solution</strong>: Extra plugins line in <code>_config.yml</code> may cause this problem.</p>
<h2 id="hexo-algolia-0-posts-indexed"><a href="#hexo-algolia-0-posts-indexed" class="headerlink" title="hexo algolia 0 posts indexed"></a>hexo algolia 0 posts indexed</h2><p><strong>Problem</strong>: Run <code>hexo algolia</code> but no post collected.<br><strong>Solution</strong>: Run <code>hexo algolia</code> without <code>hexo generate</code>. If already generated, run <code>hexo clean</code> to clean generated files.</p>
]]></content>
    
